<c74object name='sp.datatranspose' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Transpose and modify descriptor streams
</digest>
    <description>Transpose and modify descriptor streams.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.datatranspose</o> object takes incoming descriptor data (descriptors, melbands, MFCCs, or sines) and &#39;transposes&#39; it in different ways. The input can be lists or <o>buffer~</o> s and the same will be output.
</discussion>

